{"tid":2507191,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍九大司令聯名 要求擴大解密中、俄情報 助對抗資訊戰","createTime":"2021-04-28T00:28:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T09:26:23.000Z","uid":28765,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d4136d5323cd9765a7b92b39d17ed27c87e832d0","tid":2507191,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T00:28:56.000Z","msg":"〔編譯管淑平／綜合報導〕美國情報機構領導人表示，在多位四星將領呼籲下，正在研究設法擴大解密、公佈有關對手國家的惡意行為情報，以利對抗中國和俄羅斯的資訊戰。<br />\n<br />\n美國「政客」（Politico）網站26日報導，9位美軍區域作戰司令去年簽署一份備忘錄，呼籲情報機關提供軍方更多他們能夠公開的證據，來對抗「有害行徑」，幫助美國和盟友更能在現在所謂的「灰色地帶」之戰中不戰而勝，「在這場持續中的敘事戰爭中提供彈藥」。<br />\n<br />\n這份備忘錄由當時即將卸任的美軍印太司令部司令戴維森（Phil Davidson）發起，包括歐洲、非洲、拉丁美洲等區域，以及特種作戰、太空司令部領導人響應，致函給當時的代理國家情報首長馬奎爾（Joseph Maguire），震撼五角大廈、情報圈和國會。由於這9名將領的官階，這份備忘錄又被稱為「36星備忘錄」。<br />\n<br />\n報導引述多名熟悉此事的政府官員說法，美軍11位作戰司令中就有9位簽署，且其中8人都是現役，幾乎是前所未聞，此事突顯軍方最高將領不尋常的警惕程度。美軍只剩中央司令部、網戰司令部司令並未連署。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n當時也收到這份備忘錄的國防部情報安全事務副部長賓根（Kari Bingen）說，「俄羅斯，還有特別是中國，已將資訊武器化」，「這是軍方領導人和情報專業人士都在提出的一大關切」。<br />\n<br />\n這份備忘錄強調，現狀使他們不足以對抗中俄的宣傳，軍方點出，衛星影像是一項有必要擴大公開的情報領域；指華府唯有在公領域用事實應對21世紀挑戰，才能鞏固美國盟邦的支持，但是過於嚴格的保密規範削弱了這些努力。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3513686\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3513686&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0vilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=9ca7bf9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3513686&h=9dc8f6fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3513686</a>"},{"pid":"9364b4728cf0796c9dc40bd4a5417bcfd1800b16","tid":2507191,"uid":394702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:19:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8bbf28c54eafb931d99b9545cac96c5db91ca83","tid":2507191,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:25:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">由於這9名將領的官階，這份備忘錄又被稱為「36星備忘錄」。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05bbe92f0e6bf27ab647768273d85a86a33e0cc3","tid":2507191,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:26:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">美軍只剩中央司令部、網戰司令部司令並未連署。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51df2abbb972026314986a488197c387e64c892d","tid":2507191,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:28:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38824d6b73808797103fa82b43f3951174dfa626","tid":2507191,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7870089c77e4f28189d8ef797602727